title: "Ecosystem-wide PM living-context map: audit, ADRs, roadmap, and forward backlog (2026-05-31)"
description: "Establish a best-practice, living project-management map of the entire pm-cli ecosystem: forward backlog, architectural decision records, a roadmap milestone, agent/user stories, and capability epics — without duplicating the 902 historical items."
