risk: medium
confidence: high
resolution: Living-map audit synthesis completed
expected_result: "The ecosystem audit organizes findings into capability areas, decisions, stories, and forward backlog without duplicating existing pm lineage."
actual_result: "The closed Epic 'Ecosystem-wide PM living-context map: audit, ADRs, roadmap, and forward backlog (2026-05-31)' captures the completed living-map audit synthesis and links the resulting tracker structure."
